wel voldoen aan enkele verplichtingen (= gebruikseisen). </p><p><a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-de-milieudeskundige-geluid-en-trillingen\">Meer info over de verplichtingen voor erkende milieudeskundigen</a>.</p>","en":"<p>To be recognised as an ‘environmental expert in noise and vibrations’, you must fulfil:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">general recognition conditions</a> that apply to recognitions relating to the environment<ul><li>in the 3 years that precede the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, the applicant has not been convicted of a criminal offence in a member state of the European Economic Area, for infringements of the environmental legislation concerning the use of the recognition.</li><li>in the 2 years that precede the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object was revoked due to infringement of the obligations associated with that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special recognition conditions:</strong><ul><li>be a natural person</li><li>having obtained at least a <strong>master’s </strong>or equivalent degree<ul><li>having at least 3 years’ practical experience in contracts in the field of the recognition, obtained within the 5 years preceding the application for recognition</li></ul></li><li>having obtained at least a <strong>bachelor’s </strong>or equivalent degree<ul><li>having at least 5 years’ practical experience in the field of the recognition, obtained within the 7 years preceding the application for recognition</li></ul></li><li>having successfully completed a <strong>training course</strong> in which the subjects listed in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36635&amp;woLang=nl\">annex 9 of the VLAREL</a> are covered.</li></ul></li></ul><h2>Validity period and obligations</h2><p>The recognition is valid for an <strong>indefinite period</strong>. As a recognised ‘environmental expert in noise and vibrations’, you must meet the following obligations among others to retain your recognition:</p><ul><li>each year, undergo <strong>refresher training</strong> of at least 8 hours on the most recent developments and legislation on noise and vibrations for which you are recognised (noise and/or vibrations)</li><li>hold <strong>insurance</strong> for third-party liability, including professional liability, in connection with the use of the recognition</li><li>pay the<a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\"> annual fee</a>. The first payment is to be made in the year following the year in which you obtained the recognition. Failure to pay the annual fee will lead to automatic suspension of the recognition following a formal notice of default. If the fee is not paid within 30 days of the suspension, the recognition will automatically lapse.</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://omgeving.vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-erkende-milieudeskundigen-bodemcorrosie\">More info on the obligations for recognised environmental experts</a> can be found on the Department of Environment and Spatial Development website.</p>"},"naam":{"en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Voorwaarden","nl":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure","en":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Vraag jouw erkenning aan bij het Departement Omgeving van de Vlaamse overheid.</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1653046567/200204_Aanvraag_erkenning_milieudeskundige_geluid_en_trillingen_exzvwf.docx\">Download het aanvraagformulier</a> en vul het in.</li><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1653046568/20170926_MDGTinvullijst_0_ohpr4k.xlsx\">Maak ook gebruik van de invullijst</a> om jouw aanvraag vlotter te doen verlopen en voeg de nodige bew